{
  "stem": "17761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I sold this watch for two big breads, breads like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And from these breads we ate quite a good number of days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We-- we [INAUDIBLE] it and we divided it into little rations for each day for each child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember it was a Friday night and one or two of my sisters started to cry because they were hungry.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my parents took pieces from their ration and gave it to the children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was the way we started to organize ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now, the other problem was the winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "That winter we had in that place temperatures going below zero centigrades, about 32, 34 centigrades.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's a lot-- I have no idea what that means in Fahrenheit, but very, very cold, to the extent that when you touched with your bare hand some iron door handle, the hand leaked to that just because of the cold.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Many, many people just didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They froze outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "If they didn't have where to stay or if they didn't have what-- what to put on themselves, they just didn't wake up in the morning, especially if they drank a little bit of alcohol from somewhere.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was killing-- there were by hundreds and thousands of people who perished this way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is a long story.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
